We went to Wakayama Prefecture to see the ocean, the sunrise, and sunset. This sunrise is from the town of Uqui, on the southeast side of the Wakayama peninsula.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
海、日の出、日の入りを見に和歌山県に行きました。 この日の出は和歌山半島の南東側にある宇久井からです。

&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Sunrise" /><category term="Pacific Ocean" /><summary type="html">We went to Wakayama Prefecture to see the ocean, the sunrise, and sunset. This sunrise is from the town of Uqui, on the southeast side of the Wakayama peninsula.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2103_A7R03757.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Hashiguiiwa Rocks・橋杭岩</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210322/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Hashiguiiwa Rocks・橋杭岩" /><published>2021-03-22T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-03-22T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/hashiguiiawa</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210322/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Hashiguiiwa is an unusual rock formation in Kushimoto, in the most southern part of Wakayama Prefecture. A tiny island with a shrine completes the scene.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
橋杭岩は、和歌山県最南端の串本町にある珍しい岩です。 神社のある小さな島がこの岩と相まって独特の眺めになります。

&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Beach" /><category term="Shrines" /><summary type="html">Hashiguiiwa is an unusual rock formation in Kushimoto, in the most southern part of Wakayama Prefecture. A tiny island with a shrine completes the scene.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2103_A7R03711.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Through the Woods・森の中</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210320/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Through the Woods・森の中" /><published>2021-03-20T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-03-20T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/bamboo</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210320/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
